1002	1003	MIGRATE REPLICA	LOW	COMPLETED	3	FULL	3	FULL	migrate replica due to unit group not match
1002	1003	MIGRATE REPLICA	LOW	COMPLETED	3	FULL	3	FULL	migrate replica due to unit group not match
